 {'action': 'created', 'author': 'mixonic', 'comment_id': 188083702.0, 'datetime': '2016-02-24 05:38:23+00:00', 'masked_author': 'username_4', 'text': '@rwjblue and I have discussed this in person. He feels confident we can spike an addon that would detect if an app exists, and if it does not, then display this prompt.

